casebody.data:
MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

93-2263. Hicks v. Consol. Rail Corp.

Clermont County, No. CA93-03-018. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Clermont County. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that said application be, and the same is hereby, granted, effective July 8, 1994.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
